initially thinking about how I could make the most money with the tip days but then realised that I should concentrate on the toll days more and to try not to lose money instead as my mindset. I was struggling to implement an effective strategy because even when I could potentially make money on row or column days, it felt like I actually needed to do the opposite to the recommendation to try and maximise my performance. I was also worried about the toll charge of $10 if I was too slow so I think I was affected by this penalty quite a lot.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":415,\"time_elapsed\":2980931,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-372.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":61420,\"response\":{\"tips_vs_tolls\":\"It did slightly differ in the sense that I would sometimes be risky and do the opposite on tip days to expect bonus points but I would follow the row and column days more so on toll days. \"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":416,\"time_elapsed\":3042352,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-373.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":65799,\"response\":{\"rows_vs_columns\":\"I think I would follow the row days more than the column days but I had more influence on whether it was toll or tip day as my main factor for deciding which route to take.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":417,\"time_elapsed\":3108153,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-374.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":37280,\"response\":{\"lookahead\":\"Usually about 1 schedule ahead was when I would make a decision.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":418,\"time_elapsed\":3145435,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-375.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":74270,\"response\":{\"other_comments\":\"It was a really interesting experiment and also, I touch type on DVORAK keyboard so my brain was a bit confused when remapping the keys on the keyboard to memorise QWERTY again since I have no key symbols on my keyboard but I did have a QWERTY keyboard image on my other monitor.\"},\"trial_type\":\"survey-text\",\"trial_index\":419,\"time_elapsed\":3219705,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-376.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":5084,\"response\":\" \",\"trial_type\":\"html-keyboard-response\",\"trial_index\":420,\"time_elapsed\":3224790,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-377.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":69447,\"response\":{\"NFC1.\":\"somewhat uncharacteristic of me\",\"NFC2.\":\"extremely characteristic of me\",\"NFC3.\":\"extremely uncharacteristic of me\",\"NFC4.\":\"somewhat uncharacteristic of me\",\"NFC5.\":\"uncertain\",\"NFC6.\":\"somewhat uncharacteristic of me\",\"screener\":\"extremely characteristic of me\"},\"question_order\":[0,1,2,3,4,5,6],\"task\":\"NFC\",\"trial_type\":\"survey-multi-choice\",\"trial_index\":421,\"time_elapsed\":3294239,\"internal_node_id\":\"0.0-378.0-0.0-0.0\",\"final_zoom_factor\":0.7305282005371531,\"blue_key\":\"Q\",\"green_key\":\"P\",\"correctCount\":10,\"total_n_questions\":12,\"quiz_passed\":true,\"bonus_accuracy\":0.1},{\"rt\":34990,\"response\":{\"NFC7.\":\"somewhat uncharacteristic of me\",\"NFC8.\":\"uncertain\",\"NFC9.\":\"uncertain\",\"NFC10\":